</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>傳 HomePod 將有新版本　今年底或明年初面世</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/05/21/apple-to-release-new-homepod-in-late-2022-or-early-2023/parts/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=apple-to-release-new-homepod-in-late-2022-or-early-2023</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[藍骨]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 21 May 2022 15:25:30 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[配件]]></category><category><![CDATA[Apple]]></category><category><![CDATA[HomePod]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1100982</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Apple 不時推出音響產品，不過總是此起彼落，HomePod 產品線也可說是耐人尋味。最近有消息透露，Apple 正在準備 HomePod 新產品，最快在年底就會面世。</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Apple 不時推出音響產品，不過總是此起彼落，HomePod 產品線也可說是耐人尋味。最近有消息透露，Apple 正在準備 HomePod 新產品，最快在年底就會面世。<br /><span id="more-1100982"></span></p><p>據郭明錤在 Twitter 上透露，Apple 將會在今年第四季到明年第一季推出新版本的 HomePod，硬體而言跟舊產品變化不大，不過就未有透露這會是已經停產的初代 HomePod 還是現在仍然有售的 HomePod mini。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Apple would release a new version of HomePod in 4Q22-1Q23, and there may not be much innovation in hardware design. Smart speakers are undoubtedly one of the essential elements of the home ecosystem, but I think Apple is still figuring out how to succeed in this market.</p><p>&mdash; 郭明錤 (Ming-Chi Kuo) (@mingchikuo) <a href="https://twitter.com/mingchikuo/status/1527678477830598657?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">May 20, 2022</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>他表示，對於 Apple 來說 HomePod 系列智能喇叭是智能家居產品的一個重要元素，但是 Apple 仍然在摸索階段。如果消息屬實，則新產品可能會是隻改用更新晶片的加強版而非之前傳聞與 Apple TV 合併的裝置。</p><p>來源：Twitter</p><p>unwire.hk Mewe 專頁：<a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"> https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheigh